@NODE 0. "Introduction"
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
What does this little proggy do ?
It gives you som information about a window of YOUR choice.
For example: The window title, left edge, top edge, width, height,
the X position of the mouse (where you click), y position.
You can also use it to close other windows. And all values except x, y mouse
are modifiable.

@ENDNODE

